// Tax4Us Content Request Processing
const input = $input.first().json;
console.log('Processing Tax4Us content request:', input);

// Extract content requirements
const contentRequest = {
  title: input.title || 'Tax Planning for Israeli Businesses',
  keywords: input.keywords || ['tax planning', 'israel', 'business'],
  topic: input.topic || 'tax optimization',
  targetAudience: input.targetAudience || 'small business owners',
  contentType: input.contentType || 'blog post',
  wordCount: input.wordCount || 1500,
  timestamp: new Date().toISOString(),
  status: 'request_received'
};

return {
  json: {
    ...contentRequest,
    message: 'Tax4Us content request processed successfully',
    nextStep: 'content_analysis'
  }
};

parameters.text:
=Analyze the following Tax4Us content request and generate comprehensive writing guidelines:

Title: {{ $json.title }}
Keywords: {{ $json.keywords.join(', ') }}
Topic: {{ $json.topic }}
Target Audience: {{ $json.targetAudience }}
Content Type: {{ $json.contentType }}
Word Count: {{ $json.wordCount }}

Generate JSON output with:
- search_intent (informational/transactional/navigational/commercial)
- writing_style (professional and authoritative for tax/accounting)
- writing_tone (trustworthy and helpful for tax clients)
- target_audience (small business owners, individuals, tax professionals)
- goal_of_article (educate on tax topics, provide guidance, build trust)
- semantic_analysis (common tax subtopics and related questions)
- keywords (primary, secondary, semantic, long-tail)

Focus on Tax4Us brand voice: professional, trustworthy, helpful for tax and accounting needs in Israel.

=Create an SEO-optimized title for Tax4Us content:

Working Title: {{ $json.title }}
Keywords: {{ $json.keywords.join(', ') }}
Search Intent: {{ $json.search_intent }}
Writing Style: {{ $json.writing_style }}

Generate a title that:
- Is professional and trustworthy (Tax4Us brand)
- Includes the primary keyword naturally
- Appeals to tax clients and small business owners in Israel
- Is 50-60 characters for SEO
- Uses power words when appropriate

Output only the refined title as JSON: {"refined_title": "Your Title Here"}

=Write the main body content for Tax4Us:

Title: {{ $json.refined_title }}
Keywords: {{ $('Process Tax4Us Request').first().json.keywords.join(', ') }}
Outline: {{ $json.outline }}
Writing Style: {{ $('Tax4Us Content Analysis').first().json.writing_style }}
Writing Tone: {{ $('Tax4Us Content Analysis').first().json.writing_tone }}

Write content that:
- Follows the provided outline
- Uses professional, trustworthy language
- Provides practical tax guidance for Israeli businesses
- Incorporates keywords naturally
- Includes real-world examples from Israeli context
- Addresses client concerns about Israeli tax regulations
- Demonstrates Tax4Us expertise
- References Israeli tax laws and compliance requirements

Format in Markdown with proper headings and structure.

